414
00:16:59.955 --> 00:17:02.595
desconchada y llena de mechinales,

415
00:17:02.915 --> 00:17:06.115
manchada a trechos de tintas rojas, verdes o

416
00:17:06.115 --> 00:17:07.155
amarillentas,

417
00:17:07.395 --> 00:17:10.194
